description: Aaah yes, these songs would fit perfectly if you were about to shoot some people right on the head. Maybe even listening to these, will make you feel less guilty afterwards. You've got it all: 90s, 80s, 70s, 60s and even some 50s. For a more believable effect, just picture everything in slow motion.
name: Background songs when you're on a killing spree
